# CI/CD Workflow Definitions

This directory contains CI/CD workflow definitions using [GitHub Actions](https://docs.github.com/en/actions). The workflows cover testing and deployment of agent code and Databricks resource definitions (jobs, apps, MLflow artifacts).

To set up CI/CD for a new project, see [Setting up CI/CD](../../README.md#setting-up-cicd) in the project README and the [AgentOps Setup Guide](../../docs/agentops-setup.md). Ensure the `WORKFLOW_TOKEN` secret has the required workflow permissions.
